        "gg4hDzZ94-8_text": "<p>Wear them on concrete. Wear them for 10-hour shifts. If your plantar fasciitis pain hasn't improved, <strong>send them back for a full refund.</strong> No hassle. No small print.</p>",
        "ggSR692bw0r_text": "Wear them on site for 30 days. If your feet aren't better, send them back.",
